<td><a href="/wiki/File:2Dalai.jpg" class="image" title="2Dalai.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/39/2Dalai.jpg/60px-2Dalai.jpg" width="60" height="74" border="0" /></a></td>
