<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Dalai_Lama&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Goodman, Michael H. (1986). <i>The Last Dalai Lama</i>. Shambhala Publications. Boston, Massachusetts.</li>
<li>Mullin, Glenn H. (2001). <i>The Fourteen Dalai Lamas: A Sacred Legacy of Reincarnation</i>. Clear Light Publishers. Santa Fe, New Mexico. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1574160923" class="internal">ISBN 1-57416-092-3</a>.</li>
</ul>
